==English==

===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
{{en-noun|~}}

# A form of [[reasoning]], derived from [[fuzzy set]] theory, whereby a [[truth value]] need not be exactly zero (false) or one (true), but rather can be zero, one, or any value in between.

